#: ../../source/internal_api_server/dynamic_backend_management.rst:4
msgid "Dynamic Backend Management"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/internal_api_server/dynamic_backend_management.rst:6
msgid ""
"LMCache provides a set of internal API endpoints that allow you to "
"**list**, **close**, and **create** storage backends at runtime without "
"restarting the serving engine.  This is useful when you need to switch "
"between different storage configurations on the fly — for example, "
"migrating from a ``LocalDiskBackend`` to a ``GdsBackend``, or changing "
"the remote connector from a filesystem connector to Redis."
msgstr ""

